Well... you know,
I was in Jason's ear.

04:08.370 --> 04:10.895
Bravo machine,
it's missing a gear.

04:10.940 --> 04:13.374
I appreciate it, brother, but...

04:13.420 --> 04:15.809
with Jason, it's about
more than the shoulder.

04:15.860 --> 04:19.114
Come on, Ray, we've all
played hurt, all right?

04:19.170 --> 04:20.330
You remember
that, uh,

04:20.390 --> 04:23.200
convoy ta kedown
outside Kabul?

04:23.260 --> 04:25.125
Well, the night before,
I sprained my wrist

04:25.170 --> 04:26.341
punching a tree.

04:26.390 --> 04:29.564
Okay, Sonny,
why'd you punch a tree?

04:29.610 --> 04:31.601
I got twisted up on that
green raisin moonshine

04:31.660 --> 04:35.175
that the locals make, you know,
and I swear, there was

04:35.230 --> 04:37.744
this tree that was kind of
looking at me strange.

04:37.790 --> 04:39.963
You know, so we got into it,

04:40.010 --> 04:42.012
and I knocked that sucker
right out of his roots.

04:42.060 --> 04:44.142
My point being,
is that

04:44.190 --> 04:46.920
I didn't tell a damn soul
that I hurt my wrist.

04:48.540 --> 04:51.008
Well, man or tree, no one's
gonna eyeball you, Sonny.

04:51.070 --> 04:52.844
Look, man, I...

04:52.900 --> 04:54.629
Thanks for having my back,

04:54.680 --> 04:57.023
