05:16.010 --> 05:17.261
Give 'em hell, yeah?

05:25.670 --> 05:27.149
Mandy.

05:27.190 --> 05:28.669
Davis, hi.
Hey.

05:28.710 --> 05:29.972
Been a while.
How you doing?

05:30.020 --> 05:32.068
You know,
I'm grinding.

05:32.110 --> 05:35.193
World still stubbornly refuses
to give peace a chance.

05:36.330 --> 05:38.116
How are you?
I'm good, yeah.

05:38.160 --> 05:39.411
How's Jason doing?

05:39.460 --> 05:41.246
Oh, they cleared him.
Yeah, his head's fine.

05:41.290 --> 05:43.679
Good. And Bravo?

05:43.730 --> 05:46.335
Clay's two, so, you know,
he's feeling his oats.

05:46.380 --> 05:48.120
Sonny's Sonny.

05:48.170 --> 05:50.866
Um, oh, you know,
Ray's out at Green Team.

05:50.910 --> 05:52.081
You don't think he's
out for good, though?

05:52.130 --> 05:53.347
I hope not.

05:53.390 --> 05:55.119
You know,
it's above my pay grade.

05:56.440 --> 05:58.260
Oh, damn, I'm late
for my flight.

05:58.310 --> 05:59.789
Oh, that's right.
Yeah, Blackburn told me

05:59.830 --> 06:01.434
you're putting together
a new target package?

06:01.490 --> 06:02.434
Iam.

06:02.490 --> 06:04.572
Something big,
closer to home.

06:04.620 --> 06:06.611
How close?

06:06.670 --> 06:08.228
Hey, you don't have to...

06:08.280 --> 06:09.349
Mexico.

06:09.410 --> 06:11.275
Oh.

06:12.320 --> 06:14.368
Okay, no. Fine.

06:15.410 --> 06:17.412
No, but I never said that.

06:17.460 --> 06:20.418
Ma, I am not giving up
on my doctorate, I just...

06:20.460 --> 06:22.189
Mom! I...

06:24.340 --> 06:26.285
Uh_-huh.
Okay, fIne, then,

06:26.340 --> 06:28.205
j-just-- let's just
drop it, then.

06:28.250 --> 06:31.686
Mm-hmm. All right.

06:31.730 --> 06:35.473
Dinner this weekend?

06:35.520 --> 06:37.078
Oh, you're driving down

06:37.130 --> 06:39.257
to meet Clay.

06:39.310 --> 06:40.652
I don't know, I...

06:40.700 --> 06:41.917
It's fine.

06:41.960 --> 06:44.133
It's fine.

06:44.180 --> 06:45.431
No, you do not
know my parents.

06:45.490 --> 06:46.787
I have to meet
'em sometime.

06:46.840 --> 06:48.876
It's all right, this has
to happen eventually.

06:48.930 --> 06:50.704
