new nickname there.

10:46.730 --> 10:48.072
You're not
feeling it?

10:48.120 --> 10:49.678
Tell you what, why don't you
pick your own, then?

10:49.730 --> 10:51.379
No, it's bad luck to
pick your own nickname.

10:51.430 --> 10:52.909
