All right,
listen up.

10:59.390 --> 11:01.563
Hope you packed your Ambiens,
gonna be a long flight.

11:01.610 --> 11:02.736
JASON:
Where we headed?

11:02.790 --> 11:06.567
Saudi Arabia.
Three hours ago,

11:06.620 --> 11:10.704
Shia extremists took hold
of the Qanat of Shaqra.

11:10.750 --> 11:12.570
Qanats are ancient
tunnel systems

11:12.620 --> 11:14.440
that access underground
water sources.

11:14.490 --> 11:16.629
This particular qanat

11:16.670 --> 11:18.661
is at the heart of the largest
water source in Saudi Arabia.

11:18.720 --> 11:20.529
They intend to release

11:20.590 --> 11:22.717
anthrax into the water

11:22.760 --> 11:25.376
if their demands are
not met within 24 hours.

11:25.420 --> 11:28.150
What are their demands?

11:28.200 --> 11:30.464
Does it matter?
They're not getting met.

11:30.510 --> 11:33.240
So, the Saudis have asked
for our help on this.

11:33.300 --> 11:36.258
Anthrax is a self-replicating
bacterium.

11:36.300 --> 11:40.555
Released into that aquifer,
no water there

11:40.610 --> 11:42.646
ever again.

11:42.700 --> 11:44.656
God knows how many it
would just plain kill.

11:44.700 --> 11:46.827
Nothing can go wrong here.

12:12.510 --> 12:17.038
MANDY: Doza operates with
impunity and we dig holes.

12:17.080 --> 12:22.029
Corruption and indifference
are his most powerful allies.

12:22.080 --> 12:25.607
You talking to me or yourself?

12:31.310 --> 12:33.562
Hey.

12:40.540 --> 12:43.703
Well, now you found your agent.

12:43.760 --> 12:45.273
Now what?

12:45.320 --> 12:50.235
Now I transform indifference
Into outrage.

13:20.840 --> 13:23.274
Heard Bravo spun up, huh?

13:23.320 --> 13:26.790
You got that twitch.

13:26.840 --> 13:29.536
Operating's not
the only thing, Adam.

13:29.590 --> 13:31.148
But it's the
biggest thing.

13:31.200 --> 13:33.065
Is it?

13:33.110 --> 13:37.854
You know, believe it
or not, I'm good.

13:37.900 --> 13:39.800
Home life is better than ever.

13:39.860 --> 13:42.420
Regular hours. Wife's happy.

13:42.470 --> 13:46.383
Kids are happy.
Yard's looking tip-top.

13:48.430 --> 13:51.388
Told myself the same
lies for a while.

13:54.870 --> 13:56.918
What made you realize
they were lies?

13:56.960 --> 14:00.430
On my way to work,
half awake, for weeks,

14:00.490 --> 14:01.912
I'd drive to my
old squadron.

14:06.930 --> 14:10.309
I've been doing
the same damn thing.

14:10.370 --> 14:14.067
Harder I tried to convince
myself to enjoy shore duty,

14:14.110 --> 14:16.886
harder I wished I
was back out there.

14:16.940 --> 14:18.419
Feels like purgatory
here, brother.

14:18.460 --> 14:19.893
I hear you.

14:19.940 --> 14:21.453
Jason still being stubborn?

14:21.510 --> 14:25.469
I'm cleared hot, but here I am.

14:26.950 --> 14:29.680
Well...

14:29.730 --> 14:32.255
"Well" what?

14:32.300 --> 14:36.304
You hear what's going on
over at Charlie Team?

14:42.050 --> 14:44.006
Right. Our counterparts
in Saudi intelligence

14:44.050 --> 14:47.133
believe that the extremists
are camped out here,

14:47.190 --> 14:50.091
the mother well-- it's
the main source of the water.

14:50.150 --> 14:51.356
How many extremists?

14:51.410 --> 14:53.139
Could be up to 20.
Not really sure.

14:53.190 --> 14:55.055
What are we clear on?

14:55.110 --> 14:57.931
What we do know is that
this modern access tunnel

14:57.980 --> 15:00.619
leads directly
to their encampment,

15:00.680 --> 15:03.023
but the extremists
have collapsed the entrance

15:03.070 --> 15:04.765
right behind them.

15:04.810 --> 15:06.766
Well, why don't we
help them on their way,

15:06.810 --> 15:08.027
blow the damn thing up,
call it early

15:08.080 --> 15:09.763
and hit a happy hour?

15:09.820 --> 15:11.549
That's great,

15:11.600 --> 15:13.204
but the loss of infrastructure

15:13.260 --> 15:14.818
would cripple the region
for decades.

15:14.870 --> 15:17.122
There's no way
we could clear the rubble?

15:17.170 --> 15:18.558
