don't we come at 'em

15:21.180 --> 15:22.568
from a different
direction, right?

15:22.610 --> 15:24.396
There's a vertical
access shaft here

15:24.440 --> 15:26.044
on the other side
of the mother well.

15:26.090 --> 15:27.967
I say we rappel in
and we roll in quiet.

15:28.010 --> 15:29.443
