Yeah, yeah, it's Goonies.

15:56.340 --> 15:57.853
CLAY:
This is all solid rock?

15:57.910 --> 16:00.470
Yeah. Hundreds of meters,
every direction.

16:00.520 --> 16:01.953
All right, well, comms
aren't gonna work then.

16:02.000 --> 16:03.956
Oh, okay, so what's
the solution there?

16:04.000 --> 16:05.820
Line-of-sight relays.

16:05.870 --> 16:08.475
You know, we just position
some men at intervals

16:08.530 --> 16:10.612
and that way
we can ensure

16:10.660 --> 16:13.481
the execution-checklist items
are communicated back to Havoc.

16:13.530 --> 16:14.963
Yeah, we're good?
We're good.

16:15.010 --> 16:16.614
Yeah.
JASON: Sonny's
fully torqued right now.

16:16.670 --> 16:18.399
ERIC:
All right, let's
get some shut-eye.

16:18.450 --> 16:20.884
Riyadh in six hours.Let's go.

16:24.020 --> 16:26.716
Good catch
with the comms, kid.

16:26.760 --> 16:29.365
Uh, just doing my best.

16:30.900 --> 16:32.891
How's Stella?

16:34.120 --> 16:36.076
She good.
Yeah?

16:36.120 --> 16:38.168
Supposed to, uh,

16:38.210 --> 16:39.723
supposed to meet her
parents this weekend.

16:39.780 --> 16:42.123
Oh-ho, meet the parents.

16:42.170 --> 16:45.037
I bet you're hoping this spin up
lasts longer than expected.

